{"tid":1687280,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大家一齊罷睇黑警記招","createTime":"2019-11-01T17:10:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T17:43:04.000Z","uid":125515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5433b677a5c99be080bb6035882983cc7b1b1347","tid":1687280,"uid":125515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T17:10:07.000Z","msg":"好似杯葛TVB咁, 大家要杯葛埋睇黑警記招<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n消息指 #香港電台 原定參與 #杯葛 警方 #例行記者會 ，不作 #直播，並已準備好一份聲明解釋杯葛行動以及 #譴責警方 (尤其昨晚 #港台 記者遭警方惡意直噴胡椒噴劑，需要送院治理*)。<br />\n<br />\n不料經幾名主管閉門商討之後，下令同事只准杯葛警方記者會的警方發言時段（開場白）。結果港台在記者會中途在 Facebook 開始有關直播，有關聲明亦無法「出街」。<br />\n<br />\n#蘋果日報 明言杯葛，不作直播。而 #立場新聞 今日未見有直播，但未知是否參與杯葛。<br />\n<br />\n不少媒體如 #TVB、#nowTV、#有線新聞 等都有直播記者會，但非常「#吸嬲」，更有不少留言鼓勵「杯葛」。<br />\n<br />\n*港台記者被襲：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/2931954696912567\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715486135226112%2Fposts%2F2931954696912567&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8DsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=919dedc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/2931954696912567</a><br />\n<br />\n#journesis #RTHK #popo #hkpolice <br />\n<br />\n======<br />\nIG: <a href=\"http://instagram.com/journesis\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fjournesis&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8DsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=c4066dda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/journesis</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q11Pv4O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ11Pv4O.jpg&h=ba50b996&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/103602823372112/posts/951484155250637?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F103602823372112%2Fposts%2F951484155250637%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8DsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=2cc263eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/103602823372112/posts/951484155250637?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"afecc2a7a99d5610502f04f165f33a27dd980864","tid":1687280,"uid":263058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T17:10:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2da3eee7ef28afd9f0651f774beccd8eac4f634d","tid":1687280,"uid":335391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T17:43:04.000Z","msg":"全部記得者背向d大話精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}